---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Directory Website Redesign Service" description="Redesign and rebuild outdated directory websites into fast, SEO-ready, conversion-focused assets.">
  <section class="pt-24 pb-14"><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><span class="text-sm text-[#00f0ff] font-['JetBrains_Mono'] tracking-wider">REDESIGN</span><h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mt-4 mb-5 font-['Space_Grotesk']">Directory Website Redesign Service</h1><p class="text-[#8b8b9a] text-lg max-w-3xl">If your current directory is slow, hard to maintain, or underperforming in search, I can rebuild it with modern architecture, better UX, and a stronger SEO foundation.</p></div></section>
  <section class="py-10"><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6"><div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6"><h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-4">Common problems I fix</h2><ul class="space-y-2 text-[#c7c7d2]"><li>• Slow page speed and poor Core Web Vitals</li><li>• Confusing information architecture</li><li>• Thin template pages and weak SEO signals</li><li>• Plugin-heavy stacks that keep breaking</li></ul></div><div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6"><h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-4">What changes in a redesign</h2><ul class="space-y-2 text-[#c7c7d2]"><li>• New visual system and mobile UX</li><li>• Better search/filter interactions</li><li>• Technical SEO normalization</li><li>• Faster, cleaner deployment architecture</li></ul></div></div></section>
  <section class="py-14"><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3"><a href="/pricing" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-[#0a0a0f] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00f0ff] to-[#00c8ff] rounded-xl">See redesign scope</a><a href="mailto:tim@stackbasesystem.com" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl">Email current site URL</a></div></section>
</Layout>
